{"tid":730010,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"Jump 32號順位","createTime":"2018-07-05T04:59:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T19:10:23.000Z","uid":85946,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1d2fd15bf4b462ac6cf078385687eba4e5a6affa","tid":730010,"uid":85946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T04:59:58.000Z","msg":"週刊少年ジャンプ  2018年32号の掲載順<br />\n<br />\n●ゆらぎ荘の幽奈さん(巻頭カラー)           (幽奈)<br />\n●約束のネバーランド                       (夢幻島)<br />\n●ONE PIECE                                (OP)<br />\n●鬼滅の刃                                 (鬼滅)<br />\n●ブラッククローバー                       (五葉草)<br />\n●火ノ丸相撲(センターカラー)               (相撲) (中彩)<br />\n●Dr.STONE                                 (新石紀)<br />\n●ぼくたちは勉強ができない                 (學不來)<br />\n●アリスと太陽(センターカラー)             (Alice) (中彩)<br />\n●総合時間事業会社代表取締役社長<br />\n  専属秘書田中誠司                         (田中)<br />\n●紅葉の棋節                               (將棋)<br />\n●食戟のソーマ                             (食戟)<br />\n●BORUTO(センターカラー)                   (BORUTO) (中彩)<br />\n●ハイキュー!!                             (排球)<br />\n●呪術廻戦                                 (咒術)<br />\n●キミを侵略せよ！                         (外星人)<br />\n●アクタージュ                             (act-age)<br />\n●ノアズノーツ                             (Noah's Notes)<br />\n●銀魂                                     (銀魂)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n休載<br />\n<br />\n●ワールドトリガー                         (WT)<br />\n●僕のヒーローアカデミア                   (英雄)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n排球發行3000萬部、食戟1500萬部、幽奈200萬部<br />\n   新作賣比較好的就咒術，第一天銷售就擠進文教堂10位<br />\n   (第一天: 英雄1位，排球2位，食戟3位，學不來6位，石頭7位，幽奈8位，<br />\n            咒術10位，高爾夫12位，演員18位，筆記35位，ziga47位)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsource:<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/C_Chat/M.1530765102.A.638.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FC_Chat%2FM.1530765102.A.638.html&d=YQB2o1wh3sicG7IwSBx8WRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=46486c31\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/C_Chat/M.1530765102.A.638.html</a><br />\n<br />\n咒術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n外星人同Noah幾危險下"},{"pid":"f7132ce7605650b19bb40d8559ef587ed4e1a4e0","tid":730010,"uid":39256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T05:01:38.000Z","msg":"究竟五葉草幾耐出一次<br />\n漫畫人成日都冇更新"},{"pid":"444f28243d447e40ed4190b067b89fef910cf992","tid":730010,"uid":85946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T05:02:26.000Z","msg":"演員和咒術也有促銷，辦法為買單行本有機會拿到上次週刊中彩的複製原畫<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n官方說法為這活動是辦給這2部人氣覺醒的作品<br />\n<br />\n睇黎集英都想捧咒術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bc28f6e1f8cbde5b8d287fd46d9144345a97059","tid":730010,"uid":121286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T05:04:42.000Z","msg":"唉 好想見到World Trigger上返榜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 究竟葦原老師幾時先可以畫到架,就邌2年啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbd3b9a20688381d93d75f807fb264fd60a7890a","tid":730010,"uid":132605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7132ce7605650b19bb40d8559ef587ed4e1a4e0","tid":730010,"uid":39256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T05:01:38.000Z","msg":"究竟五葉草幾耐出一次<br />\n漫畫人成日都冇更新"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T05:34:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比大陸公司買咗版權 要睇就上網搵<br />\n漢化組都唔會再漢 同埋大陸公司漢化<br />\n唔一定今日出新一集 聽日就有 可能等幾星期"},{"pid":"337ed0cbb6c95f8f92b40faa359d7816081616b8","tid":730010,"uid":39256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbd3b9a20688381d93d75f807fb264fd60a7890a","tid":730010,"uid":132605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7132ce7605650b19bb40d8559ef587ed4e1a4e0","tid":730010,"uid":39256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T05:0